@startuml
title Website Pemerintah Provinsi Jawa Timur

autonumber
actor User
actor Admin
boundary UI
control System
database DB
control API
control Notification

== Authentication ==
User -> UI : Input kredensial <<E>>
UI -> System : Submit kredensial <<E>>
System -> DB : Read user <<R>>
System -> DB : Read role <<R>>
System -> DB : Write session <<W>>
System -> DB : Write audit login <<W>>
System --> UI : Status login <<X>>
UI --> Admin : Dashboard tampil <<X>>

== CMS ==
Admin -> UI : Request CMS <<E>>
UI -> System : Load konten <<E>>
System -> DB : Read konten <<R>>
System -> DB : Read metadata <<R>>
System --> UI : Data CMS <<X>>

Admin -> UI : Edit konten <<E>>
UI -> System : Submit perubahan <<E>>
System -> DB : Write konten <<W>>
System -> DB : Write audit CMS <<W>>
System --> UI : Status update <<X>>

== Galeri Multimedia ==
