System --> UI : Data galeri <<X>>

Admin -> UI : Upload media <<E>>
UI -> System : Submit media <<E>>
System -> DB : Write media <<W>>
System -> DB : Write metadata media <<W>>
System --> UI : Media tersimpan <<X>>

